478
00:33:18,977 --> 00:33:20,040
Je veux savoir.

479
00:33:21,230 --> 00:33:22,083
Explique !

480
00:33:24,710 --> 00:33:26,220
À qui tu parlais ?

481
00:33:30,341 --> 00:33:31,342
Je parle à...

482
00:33:40,065 --> 00:33:40,935
Recule.

483
00:33:41,417 --> 00:33:42,418
Recule.

